<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FX リスク管理プラン</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #111111;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  .page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

  /* Header */
  .header {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #111;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .label-small {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #555;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .basis-tag {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #444;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  /* Base strip */
  .base-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: #ccc;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .base-strip .base-cell:nth-child(4),
  .base-strip .base-cell:nth-child(5) {
    grid-column: span 1;
  }
  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .base-strip { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); }
  }
  .base-cell {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 12px 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .base-cell .bl {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: #555;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .base-cell .bv {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
  .bv.pos { color: #15803d; }

  /* Stages */
  .stages { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .stage {
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1.5px solid #ccc;
  }

  .stage-left {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .stage-left-text {}
  .stage-name {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .stage-amount {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    color: #111;
  }
  .stage-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #444;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .stage-tag {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .stage-right {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }

  .metrics-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .metrics-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }
  }
  .m-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    color: #555;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .m-val {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    color: #111;
  }
  .m-val.pos { color: #15803d; }
  .m-val.neg { color: #b91c1c; }
  .m-val.warn { color: #b45309; }

  .conds {
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    padding-top: 8px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px 12px;
  }
  .cond-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .cond-item {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #333;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
  .cond-item::before { content: "□ "; color: #888; }

  /* Stage colors */
  .stage-now { border-color: #86efac; }
  .stage-now .stage-left { background: #f0fdf4; }
  .stage-now .stage-amount { color: #15803d; }
  .stage-now .stage-tag { background: #dcfce7; color: #15803d; }

  .stage-s1 { border-color: #93c5fd; }
  .stage-s1 .stage-left { background: #eff6ff; }
  .stage-s1 .stage-amount { color: #1d4ed8; }
  .stage-s1 .stage-tag { background: #dbeafe; color: #1d4ed8; }

  .stage-s2 { border-color: #fdba74; }
  .stage-s2 .stage-left { background: #fff7ed; }
  .stage-s2 .stage-amount { color: #c2410c; }
  .stage-s2 .stage-tag { background: #ffedd5; color: #c2410c; }

  .stage-s3 { border-color: #fca5a5; }
  .stage-s3 .stage-left { background: #fef2f2; }
  .stage-s3 .stage-amount { color: #b91c1c; }
  .stage-s3 .stage-tag { background: #fee2e2; color: #b91c1c; }

  .arrow-row {
    text-align: center;
    color: #aaa;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 2px 0;
  }

  /* Downgrade */
  .down-section {
    background: #fff5f5;
    border: 1.5px solid #fca5a5;
    border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .down-title {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    color: #b91c1c;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .down-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px 16px;
  }
  .down-item {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #222;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
  .down-item::before { content: "▸ "; color: #b91c1c; }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .footer-note {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #555;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .footer-date {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #888;
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="label-small">FX Risk Management</div>
    <div class="title">リスク管理 ステージプラン</div>
    <div class="basis-tag">
      基準：1月以降 実績データ　月5回 / 勝率40% / 勝ちRR avg 1.62<br>
      月純期待 = 実績¥18,166 × リスク倍率
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="base-strip">
    <div class="base-cell"><div class="bl">TOTAL ENTRY</div><div class="bv">25回</div></div>
    <div class="base-cell"><div class="bl">WIN RATE</div><div class="bv pos">40.0%</div></div>
    <div class="base-cell"><div class="bl">AVG WIN RR</div><div class="bv pos">+1.62</div></div>
    <div class="base-cell"><div class="bl">TOTAL P&L</div><div class="bv pos">+¥81,725</div></div>
    <div class="base-cell"><div class="bl">CAPITAL</div><div class="bv">¥2,000,000</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="stages">

    <div class="stage stage-now">
      <div class="stage-left">
        <div class="stage-left-text">
          <div class="stage-name">NOW — START</div>
          <div class="stage-amount">¥30,000</div>
          <div class="stage-sub">/ トレード</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-tag">今すぐ移行</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stage-right">
        <div class="metrics-row">
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均利益合計</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥126,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均損失合計</div><div class="m-val neg">-¥72,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月純期待収益</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥54,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">最大同時リスク</div><div class="m-val warn">¥120,000</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="conds">
          <span class="cond-label">▶ 移行条件</span>
          <span class="cond-item">条件なし・本日から</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="arrow-row">↓</div>

    <div class="stage stage-s1">
      <div class="stage-left">
        <div class="stage-left-text">
          <div class="stage-name">STAGE 1</div>
          <div class="stage-amount">¥40,000</div>
          <div class="stage-sub">/ トレード</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-tag">STAGE 1</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stage-right">
        <div class="metrics-row">
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均利益合計</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥169,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均損失合計</div><div class="m-val neg">-¥96,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月純期待収益</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥73,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">最大同時リスク</div><div class="m-val warn">¥160,000</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="conds">
          <span class="cond-label">▶ 移行条件（全部満たしたら）</span>
          <span class="cond-item">¥3万で1ヶ月継続</span>
          <span class="cond-item">勝率40%以上</span>
          <span class="cond-item">回復係数1.5以上</span>
          <span class="cond-item">最大DD ¥120,000以内</span>
          <span class="cond-item">エントリー遵守率60%以上</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="arrow-row">↓</div>

    <div class="stage stage-s2">
      <div class="stage-left">
        <div class="stage-left-text">
          <div class="stage-name">STAGE 2</div>
          <div class="stage-amount">¥50,000</div>
          <div class="stage-sub">/ トレード</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-tag">STAGE 2</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stage-right">
        <div class="metrics-row">
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均利益合計</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥211,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均損失合計</div><div class="m-val neg">-¥120,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月純期待収益</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥91,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">最大同時リスク</div><div class="m-val neg">¥200,000</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="conds">
          <span class="cond-label">▶ 移行条件（全部満たしたら）</span>
          <span class="cond-item">Stage1で1ヶ月継続</span>
          <span class="cond-item">勝率40%以上</span>
          <span class="cond-item">回復係数2.0以上</span>
          <span class="cond-item">最大DD ¥160,000以内</span>
          <span class="cond-item">エントリー・決済遵守率65%以上</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="arrow-row">↓</div>

    <div class="stage stage-s3">
      <div class="stage-left">
        <div class="stage-left-text">
          <div class="stage-name">STAGE 3 — 上限</div>
          <div class="stage-amount">¥60,000</div>
          <div class="stage-sub">/ トレード</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stage-tag">上限</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stage-right">
        <div class="metrics-row">
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均利益合計</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥253,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月平均損失合計</div><div class="m-val neg">-¥144,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">月純期待収益</div><div class="m-val pos">+¥109,000</div></div>
          <div><div class="m-label">最大同時リスク</div><div class="m-val neg">¥240,000</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="conds">
          <span class="cond-label">▶ 移行条件（Stage2を2ヶ月クリア後）</span>
          <span class="cond-item">回復係数2.5以上×2ヶ月連続</span>
          <span class="cond-item">最大DD ¥200,000以内</span>
          <span class="cond-item">エントリー・決済遵守率70%以上</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="down-section">
    <div class="down-title">DOWNGRADE — 1段階下げる条件</div>
    <div class="down-items">
      <span class="down-item">最大DDが資金の10%（¥200,000）超</span>
      <span class="down-item">3連敗後にルール外エントリー</span>
      <span class="down-item">決済遵守率50%割れ</span>
      <span class="down-item">感情でリスク額を変えた</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-note">
      月平均損失 = 負け2.4回 × リスク額　／　月平均利益 = 実績比例換算　／　最大同時リスク = 4ポジ想定
    </div>
    <div class="footer-date">2026.05</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
